The number of cumulative cases rose to 20,125, an increase of 988.
The Western Cape still has nearly two-thirds of all cases with 12,888 and 2,521 in Gauteng and the Eastern Cape close behind with 2,459.
Recoveries have also risen, to 10,104 recoveries.
Dept of health
